text: To the Shores of Tripoli is a 1942 American romantic drama movie directed by H. Bruce Humberstone and starring John Payne, Maureen O'Hara, Randolph Scott, Nancy Kelly, William Tracy, Maxie Rosenbloom, Harry Morgan, Edmund MacDonald. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1943. == Other websites == * * * Category:1942 romance movies Category:1942 drama movies Category:American romantic drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by H. Bruce Humberstone
